Movie: Chicken Run: Dawn of the Nugget

Review: It was okay. I could obviously see the Hitchcock homages. It just felt weak overall. Definitely something I would not find great at all coming from a contemporary filmmaker attempting a comedic homage.
Outside of the opening monologue/shot and a a couple other moments this was rather unremarkable.  Honestly fell asleep  during it
